channel.title: I get an error when i try to run, mostly anything
channel.description:
I get an error when i try to run, mostly anything... like my source runs(i have tryed more than one source), or my client runs, and even the rsmv run.. from silentcj's modeling tut. .. ive searched for help, but everyone who had this problem, no one bothered to help them. soo can any one help me on this error please:
C:\Documents and Settings\Administrator\Desktop\New Folder (2)>java Main Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: Main Caused by: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: Main at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run(Unknown Source) at java.security.AccessController.doPrivileged(Native Method) at java.net.URLClassLoader.findClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) Could not find the main class: Main. Program will exit.
C:\Documents and Settings\Administrator\Desktop\New Folder (2)>pause Press any key to continue . . .

item.title: I get an error when i try to run, mostly anything
item.dc:creator: @RiiPiiNFtW RiiPiiNFtW
item.description:
@RiiPiiNFtW wrote:

Either means someother program is running on port 43594 or you need to set your class paths. Use the search bar for setting class paths. If you have uTorrent then close it and try to run your server. If you have anyother possible programs close them and then try to run your server.
